655
00:34:48,474 --> 00:34:49,336
Stop!

656
00:34:50,750 --> 00:34:51,680
Who you are?

657
00:34:56,470 --> 00:34:57,476
What happened?

658
00:34:59,079 --> 00:34:59,989
Who are you?

659
00:35:00,556 --> 00:35:02,036
How dare you break my good luck!

660
00:35:02,553 --> 00:35:03,503
Go away!

661
00:35:03,950 --> 00:35:05,121
I will teach you a lesson

662
00:35:05,205 --> 00:35:06,575
for protecting the beautiful girl.

663
00:35:18,223 --> 00:35:19,415
Why?

664
00:35:20,873 --> 00:35:21,815
What are you doing?

665
00:35:22,040 --> 00:35:23,230
There's must be
some kind of misunderstanding.

666
00:35:23,390 --> 00:35:24,262
You must have made a mistake.

667
00:35:24,346 --> 00:35:25,209
Get on.

668
00:35:26,190 --> 00:35:26,786
Go.

669
00:35:26,883 --> 00:35:27,613
Report to the Command.

670
00:35:27,866 --> 00:35:28,768
Miss Mu is safe.

671
00:35:37,363 --> 00:35:38,126
Hello?

672
00:35:38,210 --> 00:35:39,970
<i>Sir, there is only one here.</i>

673
00:35:40,150 --> 00:35:41,090
<i>Miss Wan Qing is safe.</i>

674
00:35:43,323 --> 00:35:44,283
Only one?

675
00:35:44,670 --> 00:35:45,840
All right. I got it.

676
00:35:46,620 --> 00:35:47,690
She should be safe.

677
00:35:48,040 --> 00:35:48,869
Xu Guang Yao

678
00:35:48,953 --> 00:35:50,823
has caught onto the bait.

679
00:35:51,893 --> 00:35:52,700
You can go.

680
00:35:53,179 --> 00:35:53,933
<i>Yes.</i>

681
00:36:03,630 --> 00:36:06,000
A boy and girl in the wild…

682
00:36:09,040 --> 00:36:10,080
It's none of my business.

683
00:36:10,760 --> 00:36:11,716
Why?

684
00:36:15,222 --> 00:36:16,858
Tan Si. Get the car ready.

685
00:36:16,950 --> 00:36:17,852
Yes, sir.

686
00:36:20,760 --> 00:36:21,859
Did you know

687
00:36:22,360 --> 00:36:25,150
when I was young, Mother always told me

688
00:36:26,230 --> 00:36:27,470
after a person died,

689
00:36:27,800 --> 00:36:29,360
he or she would become a star in the sky.

690
00:36:30,760 --> 00:36:32,040
Will my mother and brother

691
00:36:32,661 --> 00:36:33,926
become stars in the sky

692
00:36:34,010 --> 00:36:35,095
looking at me from above?

693
00:36:35,260 --> 00:36:37,660
<i>[THE MEMORIAL TABLET OF XIAO BING QING]</i>

694
00:36:40,983 --> 00:36:41,883
I believe

695
00:36:42,283 --> 00:36:43,843
they are not only looking at you

696
00:36:44,320 --> 00:36:45,106
but also

697
00:36:45,190 --> 00:36:46,390
staying with you.

698
00:36:49,063 --> 00:36:50,470
I always think…

699
00:36:51,120 --> 00:36:53,320
If they were still alive,

700
00:36:54,230 --> 00:36:55,840
I'd stay with them

701
00:36:56,523 --> 00:36:57,683
forever.

702
00:37:02,758 --> 00:37:03,591
Wan Qing.

703
00:37:04,580 --> 00:37:05,511
I am here with you.

704
00:37:06,710 --> 00:37:07,910
I will keep your company.

705
00:37:09,190 --> 00:37:10,130
It doesn't matter.

706
00:37:10,800 --> 00:37:12,080
After so many years,

707
00:37:12,230 --> 00:37:13,520
I've gotten used to it.

708
00:37:25,339 --> 00:37:26,499
Commander.

709
00:37:26,870 --> 00:37:28,360
You can't see them.

710
00:37:28,710 --> 00:37:29,840
You wouldn't be able to see them

711
00:37:29,924 --> 00:37:32,230
even if you pushed your eyes
into the binoculars.

712
00:37:35,803 --> 00:37:37,043
Xu Guang Yao

713
00:37:38,040 --> 00:37:39,470
may look like a gentleman.

714
00:37:39,840 --> 00:37:41,080
But in the temple,

715
00:37:41,190 --> 00:37:43,000
