726
00:38:00,840 --> 00:38:01,870
and go straight there.

727
00:38:01,910 --> 00:38:02,690
How about it?

728
00:38:03,120 --> 00:38:04,640
Do you take me for a fool?

729
00:38:05,430 --> 00:38:06,950
Wouldn't that be ridiculous?

730
00:38:07,560 --> 00:38:08,428
Fine.

731
00:38:09,309 --> 00:38:10,255
Let's stay.

732
00:38:13,963 --> 00:38:15,093
Stay here.

733
00:38:57,430 --> 00:38:58,563
It's you.

734
00:39:00,517 --> 00:39:01,557
<i>A single day apart</i>

735
00:39:01,776 --> 00:39:02,906
<i>seems like three days.</i>

736
00:39:04,150 --> 00:39:05,080
<i>Shut up.</i>

737
00:39:05,699 --> 00:39:06,729
<i>I've come</i>

738
00:39:06,880 --> 00:39:08,080
<i>to talk with you about something.</i>

739
00:39:08,919 --> 00:39:09,756
<i>As expected.</i>

740
00:39:10,320 --> 00:39:12,280
<i>You always have a reason for coming.</i>

741
00:39:12,913 --> 00:39:13,756
<i>Tell me.</i>

742
00:39:14,670 --> 00:39:16,000
<i>Today, when I went outside,</i>

743
00:39:16,390 --> 00:39:17,870
<i>I saw Mu Wan Ting acting strangely.</i>

744
00:39:18,367 --> 00:39:19,957
<i>I found an excuse to follow her.</i>

745
00:39:20,230 --> 00:39:22,554
<i>She went to secretly see a man
in the gambling house.</i>

746
00:39:22,806 --> 00:39:24,476
<i>It was Cui Lian Feng's nephew,</i>

747
00:39:24,903 --> 00:39:27,279
<i>a typical hooligan
who behaves irrationally.</i>

748
00:39:28,023 --> 00:39:29,583
<i>I guess they were planning to hurt me.</i>

749
00:39:30,719 --> 00:39:32,439
<i>They are in such a hurry.</i>

750
00:39:32,913 --> 00:39:33,869
<i>Relax.</i>

751
00:39:34,150 --> 00:39:36,040
<i>I will send people to
watch out for the hooligan</i>

752
00:39:36,430 --> 00:39:37,760
<i>and protect you from harm.</i>

753
00:39:39,600 --> 00:39:40,470
<i>Thank you.</i>

754
00:39:41,360 --> 00:39:42,870
<i>Forget it. It's nothing.</i>

755
00:39:43,763 --> 00:39:44,923
<i>I do it for myself.</i>

756
00:39:45,389 --> 00:39:46,959
<i>If something was to happen to you,</i>

757
00:39:47,223 --> 00:39:48,833
<i>wages for my soldiers would be gone.</i>

758
00:40:10,910 --> 00:40:12,110
<i>I'm not cold.</i>

759
00:40:13,259 --> 00:40:14,402
<i>Just put it on.</i>

760
00:40:15,910 --> 00:40:16,870
<i>Don't worry.</i>

761
00:40:17,796 --> 00:40:19,086
<i>I will try my best</i>

762
00:40:19,870 --> 00:40:20,760
<i>to protect you.</i>

